		"description": "The <allow-touch> flag needs to override the touch detection, but we forgot to add this to titanium/Ti/UI/ScrollableView.js and titanium/Ti/UI.js. We simply need to change both instances of\r\n\r\n{code}\r\nuseTouch = 'ontouchstart' in global,\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nto\r\n\r\n{code}\r\nuseTouch = has('touch'),\r\n{code}",
