						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "America/Chicago"
					},
					"body": "To test, build KitchenSink for mobile web, then open in a mobile browser such as an iOS device or iOS Simulator. Notice ScrollableView, ScrollView, TableView, Picker, and PickerColumn controls work as expected.\n\nEdit the tiapp.xml and set <allow-touch>false</allow-touch> in the <mobileweb> tag. Rebuild KitchenSink and test again. Notice those 5 controls no longer respond to touches.",
